{"tid":263642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅底端傳媒上月大裁員   6月推集資計劃料收費","createTime":"2017-05-30T07:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T09:42:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9700c94a1b0c7112d61bd361f34a5cb83d5a3cdb","tid":263642,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170530/56760659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170530%2F56760659&d=vrhZnDHKW51tj3WzTCWD%2BY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=66434728\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170530%2F56760659&h=0450b751\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170530/56760659</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170530/large/1496126011_e936.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170530%2Flarge%2F1496126011_e936.jpg&h=1f1781cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網媒《端傳媒》上月初大裁員，主要涉及編採部，其公關曾指裁員人數不足50人，否認如外界所指大幅裁減約8成人手，又指公司行政及技術人員約20多人不受影響，短期內也不會有進一步裁員行動。《端傳媒》昨晚在其facebook宣佈推出集資計劃，指計劃6月啓動，呼籲大家立刻關注計劃，登記電郵以獲得7天付費模式體驗版。<br />\n<br />\n《端傳媒》fb「小端」出post指他們將會重新出發，「上個月，端陷入突然的資金困境，許多讀者擔心我們無法撐過媒體寒冬，擔心理想由此煙消雲散。當時，我們承諾你，端只是跌了一跤，我們定會再站起來&hellip;&hellip;現在，我們慢慢站了起來，為了你，我們定不失約」。不過，「小端」未有透露計劃詳情。<br />\n<br />\n之前有傳電訊盈科主席李澤楷曾洽購《端傳媒》，但交易最終未能成事。《端傳媒》2015年8月殺入華文網絡傳媒，標榜專業、中立的深度報道，贏得不少口碑之餘，亦惹外界質疑股東背景是否紅色資本。《端》大股東蔡華是一名居港海歸律師，有消息指他與國家主席習近平關係深厚，蔡華當時回應指不能因為「見過習近平」而推論他做事是「習先生授意」。《端傳媒》執行主編張潔平當年受訪時表示，不清楚投資者投資的金額多少，「但投資人有一個承諾，會給予3至5年喘息時間，不用太擔心賺錢」。"},{"pid":"6c9bf624f0d023961fb9bacb8770ca50f078bbf5","tid":263642,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fceaa3e9e12115ce7e81149ca1cf3722205f2de","tid":263642,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:12:11.000Z","msg":"薯粉呼籲支持喎，薯粉仲一窩風捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b828d99fa137c95e441788c5eb6d7a646a731062","tid":263642,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:12:33.000Z","msg":"薯片呼籲支持喎，薯粉仲唔一窩風捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33f18bda69d29f17887f1feb20072cc3b268525","tid":263642,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"都係國家既媒體<br />\n<br />\n叫689/777比錢啦"},{"pid":"75346d404460e5b08537f29cf225a288cd53efb9","tid":263642,"uid":21249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"R維穩費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4a50c1ad947bbe9ea0dca34e17552522cf78b4","tid":263642,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"維穩都咁慳？係咪想亡党"},{"pid":"c876432dc8448e865391d24c59d95bc08734fce5","tid":263642,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e16b5eca411b8ec9e3447edd9a3b98dd895a73b","tid":263642,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>維穩都咁慳？係咪想亡党</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係慳, 而係唔比你<br />\n全中國/香港 得你一份維穩報咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28920291f65412164ac8631e7ed64e179afd9570","tid":263642,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d427a3cd77aa039e31ece495aa539c101f6143b","tid":263642,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T09:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>